  "texts": [
    "In summary, we find that the prompting method matters.",
    "GPT-3.5 consistently benefits from the contextual prompting method across different datasets, while GPT-4 and Llama 2 show more varied results.",
    "The specific prompt used can be found in the Web Appendix (see Web Appendix Table A3).",
    "Results for Few-Shot PromptingTable 4 provides an overview into how few-shot prompting impacts the sentiment classification accuracy of LLMs.",
    "For GPT-4, the introduction of few-shot prompting leads to an increase in prediction accuracy in seven out of eight datasets."
